examples.en: This eccentric friendship was fast cooling.
There is a cooling breeze which crisps the broad river.
The cooling lava continued to gutter toward lower ground.
The green meadows lay in morning chill and cooling sweats.
The air conditioning doesn't seem to be cooling the room much.
The chemical passes from a liquid to a solid state during the cooling process.
The auditorium has an auxiliary cooling system used only on particularly sweltering days.
